* File: dyingjack.scr
* Mob: Diseased Lumberjack 1086

#TRIGGER tick
Type 3
Sc
wfunc %rndnum% random 0 5
if ( %rndnum% == 0 )
   emote looks up at you begs you for a release from his tortured existance.
   halt once~
Sc
if ( %rndnum% == 1 )
   emote attempts to crawl across the floor to freedom but cannot muster the strength to go very far.
   emote slumps back against the cold floor.
   halt once~
Sc
if ( %rndnum% == 2 )
   emote vomits blood and bile all over himself.
   halt once~
End

#END